			"updated_at": "2026-03-01T13:12:28Z",
			"body": "Thanks for looking into this but I think it needs to be part of a wider feature: we'd want some kind of screen on startup where the user select various options, indeed like the editor, but also sync target, encryption preferences, etc. There are various issues about this and they probably should be consolidated into one.\r\n\r\nAlso there are UI consideration - what should we display exactly in the dialog, should there be any explanation, should we include images or screenshots for additional clarity, etc.\r\n\r\nBecause of this I would prefer to close this PR for now until all this as been specified correctly.",
